{
  "stem": "14613.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You think from day to day, from hour to hour, from minute to minute.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, sometimes, at the beginning, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, it is the same thing what I said a moment ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You think about the next minute, about the next hour.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] There-- there is certain thing which I vividly remember-- and it may be a paradox that certain things I don't remember at all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the incidents which I remember distinctly about the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] liquidation was that I was with my brother on the field, where we were watching the crops.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in another few weeks maybe, we would take the potatoes and other things for the winter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and as we watch-- we're watching guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody was there, because we have seen that there is some kind of problems arising in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is what we call [NON-ENGLISH] it means everybody does what they want.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is somehow-- we're losing the structure of organizational structure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were watching the fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then suddenly, thousands of people just came in from all the sides and overrun us, all of us, that were guarding the fields.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember, here is my brother and myself, worked the whole summer for it, to have the food for the winter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, we did not yet think about-- that we are going to be sent out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were only thinking that this is our food for the winter, which we have prepared.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's all gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Within one hour, the whole field was overrun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever it was there was pulled out, and we were left crying, and saying, what's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, of course, what was been happening, like I say, it was a disorder in whole ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
